Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.91,0:00:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出生在宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从未感受过阳光照在我脸上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未呼吸过真正的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.95,0:00:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未在水中漂浮过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.88,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都从未试过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整整三代以来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方舟维持了剩下的人类的生存
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如今  我们的家园濒临毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们  是人类最后的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100个人被派往地球
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,执行一项孤注一掷的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这的每个人都是因为违反过法律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而地球上  没有法律
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要做的只有生存
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们将接受考验
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受地球的考验
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.74,0:00:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受这里所隐藏的秘密的考验
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.05,0:00:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是  接受相互的考验
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《地球百子》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-镇定  -对他们来说我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经死了  没人在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.23,0:00:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在乎你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,议会在表决是否要处决300人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以节省氧气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.56,0:01:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无线电丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈求你了  让我去找个医生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.69,0:01:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  你不能告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.47,0:01:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我如果有人知道了会怎样  说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会被流放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.29,0:01:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要第二个孩子有什么错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方舟不可能永远维持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.06,0:01:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以法官不能允许
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就像奥古斯都大帝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像书里写的那个皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子要出来了  拿毯子来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有个妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给她起个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥古斯都大帝也有个妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥克塔维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.93,0:02:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉米  让她别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.05,0:02:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  妈  你不能睡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.94,0:03:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈  我该怎么做  妈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别出声  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  我说过了吧  没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.49,0:03:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你受到伤害的  奥克塔维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥克塔维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着方舟上几百个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能就要死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人难以入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.26,0:03:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文的燃烧棒会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无线电的成功几率肯定更大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见到奥克塔维亚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  不过那是奥克塔维亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可能出去追蝴蝶什么的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.02,0:04:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉克  我找了整个营地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我会帮你找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再找一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去看运输船
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去营地里其他地方找找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.35,0:04:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别谢我  我这么做不是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了奥克塔维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你  求求你别伤害我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你别  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要  求你了  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙儿  都过来拿把武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹独自在外已经12个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都武装起来  找不到她绝不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贾斯珀  你没必要这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们把你带回来之后你还没出过营地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:05:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉克  我必须这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要用上所有的人手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要一个追踪者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬  快出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想少一只耳朵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不能相信你在监狱里留了这么长的头发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.09,0:06:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能等到早上再剪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然来了灵感  所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想和我聊什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不急
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸上的表情可不是"没什么"的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是"我要去太空漫步"的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证不会再去太空漫步了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去休息吧  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬  我们得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我就来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发型不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有女朋友了  芬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没什么可说的了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在意雷文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你和我  我们擦出过火花
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么不能终止的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.46,0:07:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我可不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大伙儿们  快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.77,0:07:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见那个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看那上面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧棒没起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.95,0:07:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没看见那些燃烧棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道从一场流星雨你就看出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是流星雨  那是葬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几百具尸体从方舟上被送回了地球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从地球上看来就像是流星雨一般
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没收到我们的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你找到了无线电
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你把它从我舱里偷走且毁了它之后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  他清楚这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且从现在开始他得背负这后果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只知道我妹妹还在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我必须找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.69,0:08:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来还是不来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们还等什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得和他们取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,300人不够的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氧气量会不断下降
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假如我们不告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地球上是可以生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会杀掉更多人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他们别无选择  -伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要走了  咱们得动身了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须得去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该留下来修好无线电  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么修  发送器都砸碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非有零件空降下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我们无法和方舟对话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艺术品补给店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:09:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道有个地方也许能给你弄到发送器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.84,0:09:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来你要和我一起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬  没有你我们找不到她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他给缝好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊  过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:11:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那  你看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是奥克塔维亚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱们需要绳子爬上来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手电筒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要下到底下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有别人在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往那边的印记更深一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他带走了她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们带走了她  那她还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他们带走我的时候一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂地球语
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.88,0:14:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我可以肯定这意味着禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-咱们走吧  -简直疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.41,0:14:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想回去就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.38,0:14:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妹妹  我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是下地狱  我也要找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得咱们已经下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还要再骑一次小马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.32,0:15:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要骑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你想穿过丛林野地还是森林
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.47,0:15:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看方舟  贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我带出门去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.72,0:15:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊妈妈  告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不会被突击检查突击到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管好你自己  贝拉米·布莱克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你妹妹如果被他们找到会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她知道会发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉过她几千遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.20,0:15:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨这事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候我真希望自己没被生出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口  奥克塔维亚  我知道你害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.88,0:15:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而恐惧是个魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭上眼睛  然后告诉你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一点都不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能把恶魔杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门  临检
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻开门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱克女士  我们受议会之命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这进行一次随机检查
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格鲁斯检察官  很高兴见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的制服已经补好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  跟新的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么东西要给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉米的推荐信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子  你认为你是当警卫的料吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.56,0:17:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这来  让我好好看看你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-站起来  快点  -我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想不想当警卫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我数三个数  赶紧过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.37,0:17:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.93,0:17:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉米  对不起  检察官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我  -不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许当警卫能使他成长为一个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-把它收拾干净  -是  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长官  这个房间没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿到我的住处来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就给你他的推荐信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕  我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.29,0:17:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.16,0:18:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文  我知道你昨天才到这
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我们可没时间赏花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.87,0:18:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧时间拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你妈妈真像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.04,0:18:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和她一点儿都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别紧张  我是夸奖你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾比可厉害了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个吊舱就是她的主意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能和我一起下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她肯定特别伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她一直都相信你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  她真是年度好妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.44,0:19:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈几乎从来没有陪伴过我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她一无所有的时候才会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会生下我肯定是为了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.27,0:19:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿我的配给去换酒喝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你靠什么生存
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邻居家的男孩  芬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把他那份配给分给我  记得我的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.15,0:19:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到踪迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样漫无目的地找不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该原路返回
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.94,0:20:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.25,0:20:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他刚才还在这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.51,0:20:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分开找  他不可能走远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们藏在树上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.72,0:20:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不应该越界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们能回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.29,0:20:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们应该快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们试试这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么找到这个地方的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我找到的  是芬找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.81,0:21:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.59,0:21:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RF  无线电频率
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们能找到控制器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们看到只双头鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.65,0:21:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在第一天到地球上的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到天堂  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.16,0:22:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.60,0:22:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在意外中发现美好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.93,0:22:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧去拯救世界  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.77,0:22:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我们可以走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.13,0:22:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走  我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.65,0:22:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们该怎么办  他们一直追着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停地跑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.07,0:22:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跑不动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会为了他停下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.51,0:22:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们知道她在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.47,0:22:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪格斯  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗玛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.55,0:23:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  罗玛  可能还有  快停下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们把我们引到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.37,0:23:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能跑进这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.16,0:23:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去追罗玛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你绝对猜不到接下来有什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.57,0:24:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,检查呗  我要进洞了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不  坐下  坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.34,0:24:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.58,0:24:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  贝尔  我不想再听
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.84,0:24:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么美妙的月出了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.62,0:24:16.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我永远都不能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.09,0:24:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在就能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.44,0:24:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团结日化装舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分钟后开始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.09,0:24:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  本来我什么都不想说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.24,0:24:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我确定我的实习组
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.62,0:24:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,负责安保工作
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.68,0:24:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在那里看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由始至终
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.32,0:24:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在还不是守卫呢  实习生
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.29,0:24:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.89,0:24:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看起来怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.77,0:24:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘莫测
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.71,0:24:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔  妈妈怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.80,0:24:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能别担心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.94,0:24:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没等她发现你出去  我们就已经回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.85,0:25:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去走走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.21,0:25:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.36,0:27:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.72,0:27:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个不会注意到我们的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.96,0:27:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腿
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.09,0:27:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.94,0:28:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.25,0:28:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个女孩  我认识
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.64,0:28:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她在这里  那我哥哥一定也在
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.22,0:28:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你也帮帮他  他们会杀了他的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.15,0:28:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听不懂我说话  对吗  好极了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.46,0:28:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么要照顾我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.58,0:29:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在山涧底下发现的我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.41,0:29:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好我的膝盖
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.60,0:29:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.60,0:29:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.29,0:29:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.02,0:29:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停下  拜托  请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.82,0:29:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在这  罗玛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.50,0:29:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们耍我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.97,0:29:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是因为我才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.36,0:30:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他们愿意  随时可以杀死我们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.64,0:30:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就赶紧的来个干脆的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.21,0:30:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.36,0:30:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道你们在那
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.67,0:30:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想杀我们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.01,0:30:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.16,0:30:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.53,0:30:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个雾角  是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.81,0:30:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酸雾
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.74,0:30:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.34,0:30:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.33,0:30:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.03,0:30:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪个站的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.22,0:31:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳耀斑预警
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.04,0:31:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个X级太阳耀斑已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.84,0:31:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在方舟的右舷
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.29,0:31:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有公民必须立刻至最近的避难区报到
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.84,0:31:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是演习  这是太阳耀斑预警
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.40,0:31:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔  我得回家
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.90,0:31:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.34,0:31:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士们先生们  你们知道该怎么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.00,0:31:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘掉面具  出示身份证
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.12,0:31:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔  我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.66,0:31:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  无论发生什么
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.23,0:31:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都得跑回家藏到地板下面
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.29,0:31:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里  你会一如既往地安全的 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.43,0:31:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.69,0:31:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来掩护你  快
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.58,0:31:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝尔  我该怎么回家
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.94,0:31:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实习生布莱克  为何亮出武器
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.45,0:31:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摘掉面具
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.62,0:31:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长官  她没事  我已经检查过她了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.92,0:32:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都没有扫描器
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.53,0:32:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请出示身份证
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.51,0:32:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  沙姆韦中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.92,0:32:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  放她走
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.92,0:32:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为您的守卫同事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.19,0:32:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我们离开
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.24,0:32:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我做什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.27,0:32:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.31,0:32:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  出示身份证
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.44,0:32:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拦住她
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.45,0:32:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要等多久
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.47,0:32:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这管用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.81,0:32:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.14,0:32:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.45,0:32:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有雾
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.69,0:32:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是假警报
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.43,0:32:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.45,0:33:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.12,0:33:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在能跑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.28,0:33:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看不到我们  我要跟着他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.19,0:33:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢  杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.07,0:33:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.51,0:33:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼他说出奥克塔维亚在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.26,0:33:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.72,0:33:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎么知道他不会把我们领向另一个陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.13,0:33:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.14,0:33:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.09,0:33:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.56,0:33:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从地堡回来的一路上你都没怎么说话
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.81,0:33:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-雷文  -告诉我我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.52,0:34:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我芬没给你做这个
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.65,0:34:02.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我在我冒生命危险下来这里时
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.60,0:34:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没在搞我的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.63,0:34:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.01,0:34:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也为我做了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.36,0:34:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可一点不特别
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.75,0:34:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得我想这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.95,0:34:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至不知道你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.75,0:34:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以为你已经死了  雷文
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.77,0:34:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他以为你没来得及逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.46,0:34:37.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.37,0:34:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有方舟上我们认识的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.94,0:34:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没办法阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.39,0:34:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅十天  他本可以多等几天的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.97,0:34:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爱他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.03,0:35:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我压根不怎么了解他
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.54,0:36:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-贝拉米  -奥克塔维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.16,0:36:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去拿钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.83,0:36:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门罗  守好入口
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.12,0:36:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.73,0:36:55.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见习生布莱克
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.04,0:36:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是门卫布莱克了  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.64,0:37:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指挥官  这一年发生了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.56,0:37:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能进来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.38,0:37:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你亲自把我妈妈流放
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.84,0:37:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还敢到这儿来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.55,0:37:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是听命行事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.49,0:37:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找我到底有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.69,0:37:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是名优秀的士兵  贝拉米  你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.00,0:37:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机灵  勤奋  足智多谋
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.75,0:37:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不是名士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.69,0:37:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得你是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.90,0:37:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也说了你会不惜一切代价保护你妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.91,0:37:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也记得
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.62,0:37:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望这话还有效
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.54,0:37:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.04,0:37:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我下面要告诉你的是机密事项
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.47,0:37:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚哈法官批准了一项
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.76,0:37:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重返地球的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.19,0:37:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要把青少年囚犯派往地球
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.58,0:37:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共计一百人  你妹妹也在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.04,0:37:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不能这么做  这不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.12,0:37:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.26,0:37:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.95,0:37:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能给你在运输船上安排一个座位
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.83,0:37:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.85,0:38:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子很难生还
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.49,0:38:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.43,0:38:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少奥克塔维亚不会孤单
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.03,0:38:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.96,0:38:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了法官
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.21,0:38:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如我现在就把你杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.69,0:38:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我  你妹妹就得独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.95,0:38:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往辐射遍地的星球
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.55,0:38:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你会像你母亲一样被流放
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.86,0:38:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞船二十分钟后出发  贝拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.46,0:38:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你答应  我们得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.44,0:38:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.96,0:38:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么找到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.02,0:38:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们跟踪他找来的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.93,0:38:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧  在他醒来之前快走
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.34,0:38:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让他醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.91,0:38:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉米  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.31,0:38:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没有伤害我  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.86,0:39:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这战争是他们先挑起的  芬  让开
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.82,0:39:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雾角
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.62,0:39:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  那是我哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.06,0:39:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉克  克拉克在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.67,0:39:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.54,0:39:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.38,0:39:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥克塔维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.84,0:39:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬  芬
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.10,0:39:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天呐  天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.46,0:39:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.61,0:39:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.62,0:39:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉米不让我把刀拔出来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.02,0:39:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.40,0:39:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他带到运输船去  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.67,0:39:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克拉克  你能救他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.11,0:39:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不不行  得让我妈妈帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.14,0:39:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得和她沟通
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.49,0:39:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但无线电不能用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.54,0:39:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷文  修好它  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.66,0:40:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.40,0:40:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事  你快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.44,0:40:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才为什么护着他
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.98,0:40:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他救了我的命
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.16,0:40:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺中罗玛的长矛其实是用来...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.14,0:40:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你搞错了  是我救了你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.80,0:40:19.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道  他把你救活
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.11,0:40:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了拿你当活诱
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.00,0:40:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不觉得他会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.71,0:40:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得...  这就是问题所在
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.64,0:40:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们今天杀了三个我们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.60,0:40:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你当时不阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.78,0:40:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我把他杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.76,0:40:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬现在也不会生命垂危了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.76,0:40:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把你的错都安到我头上来
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.39,0:40:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬的遭遇不是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.52,0:40:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时想尽快离开  如果芬死在那
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.51,0:40:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.89,0:40:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.57,0:40:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.07,0:40:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害我被锁在方舟上
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.79,0:40:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你让我去那该死的舞会
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.02,0:40:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你害妈妈被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.99,0:40:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.65,0:41:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈会被流放是因为生了你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.88,0:41:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她会死是因为你活着
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.57,0:41:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是她的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.81,0:41:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无从选择
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.60,0:41:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你出生那天我的人生就结束了
